Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.03,0:01:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Woman] What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.74,0:01:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the heat off in Atlas too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.24,0:02:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Man] They wouldn't just\Nturn the heat off...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.15,0:02:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...would they?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.32,0:02:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- General, since the day you\Nwere appointed Headmaster,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.07,0:02:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,there have been Atlesians\Nwho are skeptical
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.61,0:02:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,of one man holding two Council seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes, which is exactly why\Nwe have checks and balances.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- We're supposed to, but lately
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.78,0:02:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you've been running\Nroughshod all over them,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.86,0:02:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,making unilateral decisions without us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.11,0:02:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- Councilman, I never intended--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.69,0:02:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- What people intend and what they do
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.94,0:02:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,aren't always the same, General.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.57,0:02:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.40,0:02:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,For how long?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.28,0:02:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,My authorization?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.57,0:02:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Check it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.86,0:02:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- Councilman Schnee?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.65,0:02:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes, I agree with everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.49,0:02:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,everything that was just said.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.57,0:02:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No, uh, no further questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.24,0:02:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm not quite done yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're afraid of something,\NGeneral. Aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.99,0:02:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- I think that's pretty\Nobvious, Miss Hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:03:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to prevent Atlas\Nfrom becoming another Beacon,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,another Haven.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.44,0:03:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yet, you don't trust your\Nown Council to help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.19,0:03:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Operating in secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.99,0:03:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the actions of\Nsomebody who's hiding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.94,0:03:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm not hiding anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.69,0:03:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- Let's put it to the test then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.07,0:03:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all aware of my Semblance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.78,0:03:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's settle it here and\Nnow, General Ironwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.74,0:03:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Here and now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.82,0:03:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Weiss] Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got the wrong man on trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.78,0:03:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I know who's been framing Ironwood,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,who rigged the election.\NAnd my father does, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been working with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.15,0:03:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is that Arthur Watts?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.94,0:03:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.78,0:03:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Watts died in the\NPaladin Incident years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.57,0:03:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Jacques] What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.24,0:04:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- Play it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.49,0:04:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Jacques] That bastard is\Ncosting me more money every day
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.94,0:04:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,with this embargo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.53,0:04:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd lay off every employee in Mantle
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.40,0:04:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,if I wasn't trying to get their damn votes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.36,0:04:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,for this Council seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.74,0:04:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Watts] What if I said\Nyou could have your cake
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.03,0:04:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and eat it, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Jacques] What did you have in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Watts] James Ironwood\Nnever recognized my genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.94,0:04:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,After everything I gave\Nhim, he still disgraced me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I simply wish to return the favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.03,0:04:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Jacques] What's in it for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.15,0:04:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Watts ] A seat on the council.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.53,0:04:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,All I need is your login\Ncredentials to the Atlas network.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.99,0:04:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You promise to make Ironwood's\Nlife a waking nightmare,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.53,0:04:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and I will guarantee\Nyou victory at the polls
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,by giving the voters down in Mantle
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.57,0:04:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,a little... 'digital push', if you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.99,0:04:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Jacques] I always knew you\Nwere a good scientist, Arthur,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but I never knew you were\Nsuch a good salesman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.07,0:04:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ironwood] Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.07,0:05:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Jacques] That, that is -- I can explain that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.19,0:05:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That... isn't real.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.07,0:05:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- Jacques, take your seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.07,0:05:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- Weiss...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- Jacques Schnee, you're under arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[Weiss] Can I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.07,0:05:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Woman] Atlas killed the heat on purpose
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Man] They'll do anything to control us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.57,0:05:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Soldier] The situation here is\Ngetting out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.53,0:05:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Please advise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.94,0:06:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- I knew you'd stoop low to\Nget what you wanted, Jacques.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.28,0:06:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- This is all a great leap, James.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.90,0:06:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- No, it's quite simple really --
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.15,0:06:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,now that I know Arthur Watts is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.32,0:06:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Working with a madman like Tyrian Callows,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.90,0:06:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,it would be easy for someone like him
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.57,0:06:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,to coordinate an unthinkably heinous act
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.07,0:06:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,like the one in that warehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.78,0:06:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Watts designed Mantle's\Nentire security network.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.07,0:06:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He used that access to hack\Nthe surveillance system
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.74,0:06:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and frame someone else for the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.36,0:06:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,All while stealing an election.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And once you became a Councilman,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.03,0:06:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,your newly granted clearance\Ngave him a backdoor
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.53,0:06:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,into Atlas' secure network.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.69,0:06:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But you probably hadn't even\Nconsidered that, had you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.28,0:06:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- The people that died that night,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.57,0:06:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,their blood is on your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.82,0:06:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- Jacques Schnee must be tried,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.03,0:06:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,not only for treason, but\Nas an accessory to murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.32,0:07:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- These are outrageous accusations.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.53,0:07:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I only intended to win the election.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I had nothing to do--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- Only?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- What else will he be able to do
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.69,0:07:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,with the access Jacques' given him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- With enough time... whatever he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- Wait... wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.74,0:07:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean the heat has gone off?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- You have to believe me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.99,0:07:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know he was planning this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.65,0:07:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- You are going to shut your mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.32,0:07:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and get the heating grid\Nup and running again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.07,0:07:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- I... I've been informed
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.82,0:07:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,that we can't get into the system.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... it's been blocked off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[Sleet] Without heat down there...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.19,0:07:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,people are going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:07:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ruby] General Ironwood?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.24,0:08:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,How bad is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.74,0:08:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- He's using Jacques' credentials.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.82,0:08:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We can follow that\Nactivity on the network.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.19,0:08:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's found his way\Ninto the Amity system...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.03,0:08:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the secret is safe. For now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.78,0:08:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But if he learns about Amity,\Nshe learns about Amity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.36,0:08:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- Can you block his access?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.82,0:08:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He's already starting to lock us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- Can we trace him somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.28,0:08:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Find out where he's hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.53,0:08:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ironwood] He's going to be mobile.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We need his access point.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to get him out in the open.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Robyn] Okay, so let me get this straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, still here everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.19,0:08:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How do a disgraced scientist
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and disappeared serial killer\Nfind each other, General?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would they target you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.78,0:08:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And why are you working so hard
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.78,0:08:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,to hide the Amity\NCommunications Tower from them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.36,0:09:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- [AK-200] Citizens, please disperse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.15,0:09:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,For your own safety, please disperse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.49,0:09:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,For your own safety, please --
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.86,0:09:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Pilot] Atlas, Manta Team Delta --
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.36,0:09:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,beginning first run.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- I used to think you\Nwere hiding something
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to protect yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.94,0:10:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can tell there's something\Nmuch bigger going on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.57,0:10:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I think it's to\Nprotect something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Us... Atlas, maybe even all of Remnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're afraid of what might happen
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.53,0:10:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,if you tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- General, the Grimm are all over Mantle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.99,0:10:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The air fleet's doing everything they can,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.74,0:10:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,but they can't easily\Ntarget Grimm in the city
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.69,0:10:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,without risking casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.65,0:10:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- This -- this is what I\Nwas afraid would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.03,0:10:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- Sir, we need ground support now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.61,0:10:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- What we need is to\Nstart evacuating Mantle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's completely overrun,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.74,0:10:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not going to be safe anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.44,0:10:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Use the fleet to get --
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.28,0:10:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- If I move the fleet,\Nthen Atlas is vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.57,0:10:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I tried to keep the kingdom safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.57,0:10:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And now we're losing everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.24,0:10:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- General?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.07,0:10:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Earlier, you asked for my advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.53,0:11:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- I wanted Ozpin's advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.15,0:11:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- And his advice probably would've been
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.86,0:11:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to keep your secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.65,0:11:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,When we first got here, you already knew
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.15,0:11:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,that wasn't the right course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.07,0:11:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You had a new plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.07,0:11:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's time to give up on that plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.74,0:11:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all falling apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.03,0:11:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- The panic you were worried about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.86,0:11:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The secrets you're keeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,They're about to be in the open anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.69,0:11:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ruby] You're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.11,0:11:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We can do this together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.74,0:11:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.61,0:11:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oscar, I think it's time\Nyou get back to the academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.53,0:11:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- I think you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.15,0:11:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- Miss Hill, Councilman\NSleet, Councilwoman Camilla,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.03,0:11:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,there are some things\Nyou need to know about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.15,0:11:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's figure out how we\Ncan help Mantle... together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- I've called a transport.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.53,0:11:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- What about Watts and Tyrian?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:11:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- You leave them to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.99,0:12:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, you're needed down below.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- Alright everybody,\Nit's time to do our jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.19,0:12:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.69,0:12:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- What she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.99,0:12:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make it happen, huntsmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.86,0:12:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ruby] Oscar?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.74,0:12:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- I--\N- I--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.57,0:12:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh, you first.\N- Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.53,0:12:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to interrupt --\N- You didn't, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.07,0:12:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- I just wanted to say --\N- I had the thought that maybe--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Both] We should tell Ironwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.44,0:12:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- I guess we're on the same page, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- Guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.53,0:12:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He's finally choosing the truth over fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We should do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'll tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who chose to keep it from him
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Marrow] Ruby!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.07,0:12:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Transport's leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.94,0:12:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- I think you're needed elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.65,0:12:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- You're sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.11,0:12:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah, I've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:12:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Both] Good luck in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ugh, kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.61,0:13:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- All right, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.36,0:13:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to stress to our new\Nhuntsmen and huntresses,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.15,0:13:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,we are prioritizing citizen\Nsafety over killing Grimm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.74,0:13:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.28,0:13:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Sleet] Is this really true?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.78,0:13:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Camilla] Ironwood wouldn't lie\Nabout something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.49,0:13:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Sleet] What do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.40,0:13:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- She... can't be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.36,0:13:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Jinn told you this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.99,0:13:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- She showed us when we\Nasked what Oz was hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.49,0:14:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would Oz keep this from us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,From the people who trusted him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.82,0:14:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- He was worried you would lose hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sorry we kept it from you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't know who to trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.53,0:14:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured you should know\Nbefore you make any... sacrifices.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.32,0:14:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.65,0:14:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.74,0:14:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All we can do for the moment
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.74,0:14:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,is what we can to save Mantle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.03,0:14:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what's in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.90,0:14:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- He'd be proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're bringing the hope that\NAtlas was meant to inspire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A city in the sky is held\Nto a higher standard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- You say that like you were there --
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.90,0:14:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Our transports are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.53,0:14:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We should move.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.03,0:15:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oscar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.61,0:15:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No more surprises, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.19,0:15:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure I could take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.07,0:15:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- You and me both.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.86,0:15:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Marrow] Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- I can't shake it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.65,0:15:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- I don't think we're staying airborne.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.40,0:15:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's time to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.86,0:15:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- You have your team assignments.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.36,0:15:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.53,0:15:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- Harriet, don't stay too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.86,0:15:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah, thanks for the tip.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- Try to keep up, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- Show off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.11,0:16:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Jacques] How dare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.53,0:16:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is highly unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.44,0:16:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not stand for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.78,0:16:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.99,0:16:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be reporting this rough treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.90,0:17:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Cinder] Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.00,0:17:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're back early.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.40,0:17:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me you found what\Nwe've been looking for.
